replies.body:
Ultimate hat was a bit overkill, we didn't really need ultimate hat in the past just now it's an option.

If anything this makes ults better, since it practically gives eve her ult and run back from frost fang builds, rengar can ult further away, champs that need to stick with ults like swain can chase when they cast it better, etc.

Also its way better then ultimate with stuff like these: {{champion:76}} {{champion:126}} {{champion:133}} {{champion:60}} {{champion:9}}{{champion:77}}
